00:03:34.088 --> 00:03:36.930
An apology is a remembering.

00:03:36.954 --> 00:03:39.426
It connects the past with the present.

00:03:39.450 --> 00:03:42.712
It says that what occurred
actually did occur.

00:03:43.838 --> 00:03:48.203
